<description>
<p>Surefire reports for EUnit (Format used by Maven and Atlassian  
Bamboo for example to integrate test results). Based on initial code  
from Paul Guyot.</p>
 
  <p>Example: Generate XML result file in the current directory:
  </p><pre>     eunit:test([fib, eunit_examples],
                [{report,{eunit_surefire,[{dir,"."}]}}]).</pre></description>
